Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:05.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}とても大好きで　少し切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:10.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}でも　止まることができなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:12.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}嫌いになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:22.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}例え大切な君の傍でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:26.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:32.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見える景色は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:38.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}同じにはできないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:49.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心も未来も笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:53.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そう　まだ見ぬ愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:23:00.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}more　Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:04.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
