Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:13.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I can't believe you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.07,0:23:17.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You see one life tonight
