Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:22.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便在重要的你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:32.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}收入眼底的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:38.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不可能尽然相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:49.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论心意 未来还是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:53.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}对 还有素未谋面的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:10.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:21.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}虽然会有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:28.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永恒和如烟以及孤单的夜晚
